metadata.name: CHRONONAUTS
metadata.description:
Two friends with a dream to share,  
To travel through time without a care.  
They studied hard and worked together,  
Their passion strong, their bond forever.

They gave their all to make it real,  
To journey through time, to see and feel.  
They knew the risks and challenges they'd face,  
But their dream was worth the risk they'd embrace.

And so they built a portal of their own,  
To explore new worlds and time unknown.  
They stepped inside with hearts ablaze,  
Ready for the adventure, ready to amaze.

Their journey began, through time and space,  
Discovering wonders and a new time's embrace.  
They found joy in their dream come true,  
And knew their destiny, forever anew.
